attributes.comment:
The family is ten people they need ten green cards for ten people. So it will be ten
thousand dollers for the family. It is too much to pay. It is too hard. One or two
people might be students that don't work, but they still need green cards. What
will the government or immigration do to help these people? Even if they work part-
time it is not enough. It is too much money so people will wait until immigration
changes this or people will wait forever and never get green cards. People are
confused about $900 for green cards. People are afraid.

Comment on FR Doc # E7-01631
